Description: Small floating Pomodoro and countdown timer for XFCE
 Tiny Pomodoro XFCE is a small floating GTK timer for Xubuntu/XFCE.
 It supports Pomodoro mode, countdown timer mode, notifications,
 dark mode, autostart, and optional shutdown scheduling.

